Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate if it splashed on my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I followed the recipe exactly.\NJust like a science experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think, cooking and\Nexperiments might be similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that, each time I bathe,\Nyou always come to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it excites me when there's only a door\Nbetween me and a naked girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, it's easier to talk\Nwhen you can't see their face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know what the other Futaba is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you heard something from the fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, how I got there is a bit complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made that account before summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't know what to write about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't anything have been okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "I'm in love with a handsome guy\Nwho has a girlfriend," or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to make friends online?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been simpler than that,\Njust wanting someone to give me attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, starting with lewd stuff isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More like, you were confident about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was only an inferiority complex,\Nnever confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My feminine parts developed\Nbefore any of my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized how all the monkey-like boys\Nlooked at me, I began to hate my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like a truly filthy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, those photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I get reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt some salvation in that there was\Na reaction, regardless who it was from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as saying you got something,\Njust not how you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why. In the end, I couldn't\Ndetach from the disgust I felt being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The immense stress from the contradictory\Nends and means caused my separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\N"the Futaba that wants attention,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and , "the Futaba that can't forgive\Nthe means to do so," split apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty much it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other Futaba seems\Nto be uploading her selfies still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like her to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to school again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll have a leisurely chat\Nwith the other Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do some tedious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doka-chan, what's your favorite thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like the actress Mai Sakurajima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}She's a thing!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Most folks would say things\Nlike "strawberries" or "bean daifuku."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, what are you doing for your bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Then, the strawberry daifuku Mai Sakurajima\Nwas eating in one of her TV dramas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think, you mentioned\Nyou had something to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? Dating is prohibited!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we have to break up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't say that much, but the agency\Nordered me to not see you privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They might be confusing me for an idol singer\Nwho can't have romantic relationships at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you agree to those terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I can decide by myself,\Nso I held on the reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a problem for both of us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "nothing we can do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strategic retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with that?\NEven if you can't see me for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, you just resumed your career in show-biz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't you be more well liked\Nif you acted the model student for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A boring, yet sound argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 4th
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered that you're amazing\Nwhen you take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to lecture me, saying something\Nlike, "Don't do such foolish things."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if. That's so tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san went home,\Nand I can't go on dates with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm bored, and thought to spend\Nsome leisurely time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you came to do something\Neven more tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So did you take anything\Nother than the ones you uploaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they're not all lewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no intent on\Nshowing anyone anything, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted an objective look at myself\Nand think, "I'm doing something stupid."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A form of self-mutilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able to understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other Futaba said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa, which side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on Futaba's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretentious answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really should give up\Non one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world doesn't need two Rio Futabas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I went out to Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With my other self?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were having a leisurely chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you think of a way to return to one self?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're both doing separate things,\Ngaining different memories and experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we can return to one being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 5th
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you decided\Nwhich one of us you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's something for you\Nto decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should make your own decisions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A sound argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta! Air, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, Kunimi is asking you to fan him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba! Air, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-san, would you like some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So how long are you going\Nto keep doing stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 12th
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until Futaba no longer does stuff\Nlike that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I wouldn't mind if it's until\Nyou start showing lewd pics to only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your goal,\Nyou're getting further away each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone responding to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THAT'S A MINEGAHARA HIGH\NUNIFORM, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'M CLOSE BY TODAY,\NSO HOW ABOUT WE MEET UP?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IF YOU DON'T SEE ME,\NI'LL TELL YOUR SCHOOL WHAT YOU'RE DOING.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WHERE ARE YOU RIGHT NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'M CALLING THE POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you home, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That account... Please, delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see a really cute side of you,\Nso I'll be bragging to Kunimi sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I want you to stay with me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's in Germany for a conference.\NMom's somewhere in Europe for a business deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a line I'd usually hear in a TV drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happens a lot in our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full disclaimer, though. I am a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll report to Sakurajima immediately,\Nincluding things that didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it to things that really happen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I have you and Kunimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I felt like I'll end up\Nalone again, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't this uneasy\Nbefore entering high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether at school or at home,\Nit was a given that I'd be by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I entered high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And ended up in the same class\Nas you and Kunimi in the first year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I've felt uneasy ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi is such a sinful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're responsible for half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can\Ncome to school every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The whole school gives you the cold shoulder\Ndue to the hospitalization rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is avoiding me?\NIsn't that a bit too self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's going too far, at all.\NIs your head all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're coming to school\Nbecause it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, you're amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk to me like this,\Nyou're quite amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, stuff like that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Kunimi got a girlfriend,\NI became really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All he does is make you sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd never give me attention again\Nafter finding such a beautiful girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to have you stick around as my friend\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That, and you really don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the hots for Kunimi,\Nbut you don't understand him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you just how amazing he is.\NYou'll fall in love all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! This late at night,\Nhe'll think I have no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba's in a pinch!\NCome to Honkugenuma Station right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're just too quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said\Nto come flying over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta didn't do anything\Nweird to you, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I totally thought that you assaulted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the assailant\Nbe the one calling you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because your guilty conscience\Nwas tormenting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sakuta doesn't have a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi, don't make her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Kunimi's fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba sure is cute when she cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I last cried...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't alone at all... I wasn't alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're buying Futaba and I some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the one being exploited?\NI don't flippin' get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta rehydrate what we've lost, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa's been totally domesticated\Nby Sakurajima-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta can be valiant in the strangest places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's strong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say a typhoon\Nis coming in tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get closer, Kunimi.\NBlock the wind with that big body of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's lit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fling it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi, you're not asking me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Sakuta called me out,\NI wondered what the hell was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when I saw you crying like that,\NI didn't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Damn, I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll get a good view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks festival at Enoshima\Nis next week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we watch it together again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't made a promise\Nwith that cute girlfriend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're kind of in the middle of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't promise Sakurajima-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her agency,\NI'm prohibited from going on dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like a super-popular celebrity. Futaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the sky a bit brighter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never pulled an all-nighter before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something stupid, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're certainly doing something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been great if you two were girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The trains should be moving by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was fun. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still scared,\NI'll stay with you again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine on that front. It's my other self.\NShe has it worse than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because she hates me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, please... Take care of my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. She said she deleted the account.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she'll be doing that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill you in on the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm tired and going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 13th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Futaba in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did she step out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right after you came home,\Nshe said she was going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! She left her phone behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst feeling, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got home, passed out, and when I woke up,\Nshe was clean outta my house, stuff and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this just in case,\Nbut we're not back to one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any idea where she might have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is so tedious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba is so tedious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was a hell of a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday... oh wait, this morning.\NThere was something I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go see fireworks next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks festival at Enoshima.\NWe went last year, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi said he'd come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You already got plans or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll disappear from your sight, Azusagawa.\NI'll disappear from this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world doesn't need two Rio Futabas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My other self is being a much better\NRio Futaba than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's accustomed to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be resolved if I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wrong answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No part of that is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totally wrong. Right from the foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so, why was such a picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm shown such an enviable picture,\Nthat's the only way I can think!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere I belong anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more need for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and Kunimi are fine\Nas long as my other self is around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so insensitive, Azusagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass. You say that after all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're already fully aware\Nthat I'm insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, we're all meeting up at Kugenuma-\NKaigan Station at 6:30 on the 19th, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you ran around\Nin the pouring rain, getting soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The test results said there's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so captivated?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With such a beautiful senpai here,\NI couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're acting like that,\Nyou're definitely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I troubled you with this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.\NThe way you do this is so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave you collapsed\Nin a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so, it was worth collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about how you're no longer needed,\Nor everything will be reconciled if you fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or you're scared and not sure what to do,\Ntedious stuff like that, I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if you hate yourself, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always live thinking,\N"well, I guess this is how things go."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, this is where people say\N"You can slowly work on liking yourself,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or "There are tons of good things\Nabout you, Futaba," or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Living with such a positive attitude\Nis so exhausting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the worst, Azusagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow, it's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, such a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go see the fireworks, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come if you ask like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to see the fireworks, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I met up with Azusagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, well... I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the fireworks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should head back\Nto the consultation room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sakurajima-senpai is waiting for you, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're back to being one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. So, about the fireworks.\NDon't you dare be late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGUST 19th
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You went back to glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good with the yukata. Right, Sakuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks kinda erotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kunimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hated wearing a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother answering.\NI already know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you said anything, I think I'd cry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, Sakuta will lend you\Na sleeve of his yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can blow your nose in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go make up with your girlfriend.\NI'm sure the reason is me or Azusagawa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I guess I'll call her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you, Sakuta.\NYou rascal!
